                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Toss 'N' Turn Spear"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Yuegui: Throwing Mode</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/25750596/c587e90a155d07517365218aff66911c_7462231150818776354.png",
                "id": "talent17367",
                "key": "Raphanus Sky Cluster",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Raphanus Sky Cluster"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span> dan menciptakan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Adeptal Legacy</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Adeptal Legacy</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Setelah bertukar Karakter:</span> Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #99FF88\">Dendro DMG</span> dan memulihkan 1 poin HP Karakter Aktifmu.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/25750596/37972e3c3e9c9134cd6b1357f57aa711_6964349035443308938.png",
                "id": "talent48025",
                "key": "Moonjade Descent",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Moonjade Descent"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FFE699\">Dendro DMG </span>dan memulihkan 1 poin HP Karakter yang telah menerima DMG paling banyak.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6481254313760459070.png",
                "id": "talent35959",
                "key": "Yuegui: Throwing Mode",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/25750596/0f3a979856a1d439f1f85900b98bf648_6886936658676065786.png",
                "title": "Yuegui: Throwing Mode"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Dendro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] yang memberikan +2 poin DMG ke kasus Pyro atau Electro DMG berikutnya</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, membuat [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] yang akan mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG di akhir Ronde (Jumlah penggunaan 1 kali, maksimum 2 tumpukan)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] yang memberikan +1 poin DMG ke 2 kasus Dendro DMG atau Electro DMG berikutnya</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/25750596/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_3743879915899163681.png",
                "id": "talent85480",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_8839172750310105858.png",
